Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.23,0:01:38.20,title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(838,631)}{\fad(280,300)}第 5 話  『不可以接吻哦？』
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.07,0:01:37.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.95,0:01:40.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}啊 沒什麼啦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.66,0:01:41.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.66,0:01:44.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}對了 我想要跟你交換一下
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.75,0:01:48.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}等 等一下！ 現 現在不行
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.79,0:01:53.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是的 山田這傢伙有事要處理
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.75,0:01:56.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}如果你想這麼想親 就來親我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.42,0:01:57.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}親你和親他怎麼能一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.84,0:02:00.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}總 總之 你能再等我一下嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.22,0:02:05.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這樣啊 在午休時交換也是可以的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.35,0:02:11.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你要找小田切的話 她不在這哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.15,0:02:14.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那她會在哪兒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.03,0:02:15.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.74,0:02:18.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}寧寧沒有來過
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.45,0:02:23.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}快 快
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.66,0:02:25.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我幫她做了午餐便當
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.83,0:02:27.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}小田切同學會很喜歡的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.79,0:02:30.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}喂 你們剛才說了小田切 對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.58,0:02:32.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.50,0:02:33.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}山田
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.29,0:02:35.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}快跑
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.50,0:02:36.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.17,0:02:41.18,special-05-01,NTP,0,0,0,,{\frz203.6\pos(673,324)}最高     機密
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.59,0:02:41.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.55,0:02:43.80,special-05-01-01,NTP,0,0,0,,{\move(514,576,543.333,534.667,27,2279)\frz310.3}最高機密
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.80,0:02:46.43,special-05-02,NTP,0,0,0,,{\frz28.28\pos(586,158)}成績排名冊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.85,0:02:46.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}成績名單？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.68,0:02:49.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}總覺得不太妙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.85,0:02:53.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}喂 那邊是舊校舍啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.61,0:02:54.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}山田
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.15,0:02:55.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}白 白石
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.44,0:02:58.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我想差不多要跟你交換身體
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.99,0:03:00.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那個…我似乎還需要一點時間
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.74,0:03:03.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你遇到什麼問題了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.91,0:03:05.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那樣的話 我來幫你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.41,0:03:08.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}沒什麼大不了啦 沒問題的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.16,0:03:09.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那麼回見啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.04,0:03:10.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}等等
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.79,0:03:15.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你該不會厭倦了跟我交換身體吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.38,0:03:25.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}對不起 我們拿的成績靠前的名單被山田搶走了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.26,0:03:28.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}沒事 更重要的是 你有沒有受傷？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.72,0:03:29.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}沒 沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.89,0:03:31.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那個 這是要給你的便當
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.06,0:03:34.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我等一下吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.69,0:03:36.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}謝謝你們
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.48,0:03:38.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.15,0:03:43.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我們 小田切寧寧親衛隊 絕對效忠於您
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.53,0:03:44.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}絕對效忠
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.03,0:03:46.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那麼 失陪了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.57,0:03:47.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.75,0:03:54.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}他們真沒用
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.83,0:03:59.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}昨天就已經知道白石麗沒有參加模擬考了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.96,0:04:02.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不知道有沒有對宮村造成傷害
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.38,0:04:05.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}山田對我來說反而更有用
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.97,0:04:07.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真是讓人不爽
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.35,0:04:08.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.18,0:04:10.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}為什麼要和山田接吻
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.77,0:04:14.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}如果你想利用他 還不如用我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.40,0:04:17.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真是的 你在吃醋嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.15,0:04:19.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}才 才沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.02,0:04:22.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}魅惑那傢伙 並沒有什麼壞處
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.24,0:04:25.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這也會減少宮村的追隨者
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.24,0:04:29.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你要是這樣說的話 我也只能聽從了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.12,0:04:33.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}話說回來 他還真慢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.12,0:04:34.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我說的是山田
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.54,0:04:39.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}按理說那傢伙應該迷上我到處在找我了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.75,0:04:41.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但是他完全沒有出現
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.80,0:04:46.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那白癡 可能還沒有注意到他喜歡上你了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.60,0:04:53.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}此外 山田不知道舊校舍是我們的基地
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.14,0:04:55.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}雖然是沒錯啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.60,0:04:59.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不過能想辦法解決這些問題 才是我的魅惑能力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.61,0:05:03.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我說 果然他根本就沒來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.57,0:05:08.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我們故意跑出來 好讓他能馬上找到
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.24,0:05:15.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}難道說…我的魅惑能力對他無效？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.62,0:05:17.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這種事之前曾經發生過嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.42,0:05:19.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那倒是沒有…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.71,0:05:22.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那他為什麼不來？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.00,0:05:26.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}總而言之 我們還是先等他出現吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.26,0:05:28.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}沒錯 就如你所說
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.09,0:05:31.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但我再也受不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.10,0:05:34.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}因為這實在太奇怪了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.10,0:05:37.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不 不 所以說…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.31,0:05:43.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}另外我整天都想著山田 怎麼也克制不了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.57,0:05:44.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我要去找他
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.07,0:05:46.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}啊 喂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.45,0:05:50.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一直想著山田？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.24,0:05:52.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}到底怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.99,0:05:58.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這樣啊 所以你的能力變了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.12,0:06:01.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但是 太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.75,0:06:04.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我以為你把我當成了麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.59,0:06:05.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}才不是 沒有這回事的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.76,0:06:12.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我應該早點告訴你的 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.93,0:06:15.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}吶 山田
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.43,0:06:18.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}吻我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.19,0:06:20.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你 你說什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.40,0:06:21.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你有在聽我說的話嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.40,0:06:24.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你知道親了我之後會發生什麼事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.73,0:06:25.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是 我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.07,0:06:28.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}所以 我想試試
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.86,0:06:30.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}為…為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.70,0:06:32.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}難道是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.24,0:06:35.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}喜歡上我也無所謂麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.54,0:06:40.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真是的 結果如何我可不管啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.71,0:06:46.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}啊？ 我們交換了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.67,0:06:49.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}喂 我們這不是交換了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.09,0:06:52.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}果然 就是這麼一回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.18,0:06:55.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}什麼「就是這麼一回事」啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.85,0:07:02.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}聽好了 山田 你不能再親小田切 知道了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.31,0:07:07.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這還真令人意外 你知道他們之間的關係嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.03,0:07:11.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}喂 小田切
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.16,0:07:16.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}喂
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.54,0:07:20.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}果然我的能力對山田沒有效果
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.79,0:07:21.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}似乎是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.37,0:07:24.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}難道 你…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.47,0:07:33.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}果然 你已經愛上了山田
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.89,0:07:37.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}為什麼 事態會演變成這樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.26,0:07:40.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這樣簡直是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.23,0:07:43.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就像是著了自己的道了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.98,0:07:47.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}現在我要按順序解釋事情的來龍去脈
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.32,0:07:48.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}仔細聽好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.23,0:07:50.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}哦 哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.65,0:07:55.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}首先 魅惑他人的能力 這是小田切的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.32,0:07:56.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}確實是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.20,0:08:02.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}等一下 我為什麼會有小田切的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.87,0:08:05.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}因為那是你的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.83,0:08:07.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我的能力不是交換身體嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.00,0:08:11.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}錯了 你的能力是複製
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.34,0:08:12.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}啊？複製？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.09,0:08:14.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}複製…就是那個複製嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.18,0:08:16.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}複寫複製的意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.93,0:08:21.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}沒錯 你能將接吻對象的能力複製過來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.85,0:08:24.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這樣的話 那交換身體的能力是哪裡來的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.73,0:08:27.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}山田 仔細想想
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.94,0:08:28.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是 是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.48,0:08:33.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}回想一下 是誰跟你第一次交換身體的？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.32,0:08:39.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就是這麼一回事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.08,0:08:41.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那是我的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.37,0:08:47.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你一直在用的是從我這裡複製的互換能力
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.29,0:08:50.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不會吧 真的假的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.02,0:09:04.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.52,0:09:10.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}山田你這混帳 你對小田切寧寧做了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.69,0:09:13.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我做了什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.15,0:09:17.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}應該問你幹了什麼才對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.83,0:09:25.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這裡沒有人認識我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.21,0:09:27.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}沒人會想跟我打架
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.75,0:09:32.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}現在我終於能過著普通學生的生活了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.30,0:09:34.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我會改變的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.55,0:09:36.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}喂
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.05,0:09:38.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}為什麼你在這裡 龍
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.72,0:09:41.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}潮？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.81,0:09:46.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}醜話說在前頭 我可不想和你有什麼瓜葛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.98,0:09:50.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那是當然 也請你不要來煩我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.02,0:09:54.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}喲 你們在看什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.82,0:09:56.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}漫畫什麼的我也很喜歡的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.65,0:10:00.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這是啥？咒語？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.87,0:10:03.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你也喜歡古典文學嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.74,0:10:06.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好吧 在聽音樂的那些傢伙應該可以…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.46,0:10:11.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你怎麼看？這英語對話超容易理解的 是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.54,0:10:14.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}文藝復興對於人體的表達好棒呢 對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.51,0:10:22.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}可惡 沒有一個趣味相投的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.80,0:10:24.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎麼會這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.14,0:10:26.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你 你也是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.64,0:10:33.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}活該 說到底你這樣的人就不該來這樣的學校
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.11,0:10:35.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你可沒有資格說我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.07,0:10:37.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你說什麼 混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.95,0:10:44.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}算了 這才第一天而已
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.87,0:10:46.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好戲還在後面呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.12,0:10:52.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}到頭來 每天都是我們兩個人在一塊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.54,0:10:56.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這學校的人都好無趣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.09,0:11:01.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}沒辦法 原本他們的世界就和我們的不同
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.72,0:11:04.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}可惡 這三年都得像這樣過嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.93,0:11:06.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}看來就是這樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.47,0:11:07.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.02,0:11:11.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但那並非意味著每天都那麼無聊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.15,0:11:15.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.32,0:11:24.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你這傢伙到底怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.57,0:11:27.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}為什麼你那麼執著於那個女人？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.79,0:11:31.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}再說是你先遠離我的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.83,0:11:33.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}而你現在又出現…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.46,0:11:34.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}閉嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.29,0:11:38.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是你先找茬的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.46,0:11:40.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}啊？什麼找茬？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.26,0:11:44.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那為什麼小田切寧寧會愛上你？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.68,0:11:45.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}哈？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.35,0:11:49.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這樣啊 原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.85,0:11:56.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}所以你說山田複製了小田切的魅惑能力
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.52,0:11:59.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}然後她因此愛上他了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.03,0:12:01.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就是那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.78,0:12:02.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那這樣事情就簡單了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.86,0:12:05.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}為了讓小田切恢復正常
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.20,0:12:08.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}只要讓她再親山田一次就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.29,0:12:12.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}山田會再次複製到她的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.33,0:12:15.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}然後取消她的受惑狀態
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.13,0:12:17.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}哦 原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.29,0:12:20.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}其實你還是不明白吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.84,0:12:23.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好 我帶小田切寧寧過來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.92,0:12:24.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這樣就沒有問題了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.59,0:12:26.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我拒絕
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.64,0:12:28.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}什…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.68,0:12:33.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}少開玩笑了 為什麼我得聽你發號施令？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.64,0:12:37.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}山田 你這麼做不好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.69,0:12:41.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這些傢伙害我們吃了多少苦頭
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.65,0:12:44.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}雖說是這樣 不過…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.74,0:12:45.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}如山田所說
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.57,0:12:49.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我為至今為止對你所做的一切道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.49,0:12:54.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}當然 我會刪掉校外旅行的照片
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.50,0:12:57.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}讓我們從下次學生會長選舉中退出也是可以的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.42,0:13:01.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}所以 拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.38,0:13:03.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}讓小田切恢復原來的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.01,0:13:12.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}誰管你啊 我們走 白石
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.39,0:13:15.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}根本沒必要搭理這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.98,0:13:21.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}可以 我會讓小田切恢復原樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.57,0:13:24.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你擅自說什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.86,0:13:28.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我只是回答了理所應當的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.16,0:13:31.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}為什麼你要自作主張啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.03,0:13:37.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那你以後一直都要被小田切喜歡 也沒問題嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.33,0:13:39.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.13,0:13:43.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}她一生都要持續這段無法實現的戀情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.17,0:13:45.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.55,0:13:52.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}話說你不會是在嫉妒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.69,0:14:02.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}適可而止吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.36,0:14:05.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你不是在生小田切的氣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.19,0:14:07.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}只是在和潮君賭氣而已
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.15,0:14:09.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.45,0:14:13.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那就讓小田切恢復過來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.99,0:14:16.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}還是說你還要繼續跟他賭氣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.91,0:14:18.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}都說了不是了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.84,0:14:25.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.71,0:14:27.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我做還不行嗎 真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.30,0:14:31.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.22,0:14:35.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那麼放學後再到這裡來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.10,0:14:37.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.06,0:14:45.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}喂  潮 你和小田切接吻了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.32,0:14:48.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯 接吻了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.49,0:14:54.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那你自己也該知道她的能力是魅惑了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.24,0:14:56.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這樣也沒關係嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.74,0:15:01.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}沒關係 我很喜歡現在的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.26,0:15:08.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}喂 山田
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.51,0:15:12.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那個是我們學校的學生吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.26,0:15:12.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fs35}{\an8}不要靠過來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.38,0:15:13.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\an8}有什麼關係嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.30,0:15:15.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你們看什麼看
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.64,0:15:18.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你們想跟我們打架嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.52,0:15:23.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}竟敢小看我 那就跟你們玩玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.48,0:15:25.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}喂 引發暴力事件不好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.07,0:15:27.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那你就乖乖在那看著吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.36,0:15:31.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真是沒轍啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.49,0:15:38.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}還真是棘手的傢伙呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.99,0:15:41.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}咦 被救的女孩不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.08,0:15:45.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一周的禁閉？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.50,0:15:49.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}而且受處分的只有我 這是怎麼回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.76,0:15:51.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}昨天的暴力事件
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.72,0:15:54.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}都是你單獨行動而導致的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.72,0:15:56.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}什麼 單獨？！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.10,0:16:01.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}證人有兩個 一個是我們高中的女學生
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.43,0:16:08.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}另一個是和你一起行動的五十嵐潮
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.03,0:16:11.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是山田
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.19,0:16:12.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.28,0:16:13.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}聽說受到停學處分啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.86,0:16:14.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}果然啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.24,0:16:19.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}喂 潮
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.84,0:16:34.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}也就是說 你在學校裡被人討厭是因為小田切同學啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.93,0:16:36.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這是多麼的悲劇啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.39,0:16:37.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}明明只是個山田而已
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.05,0:16:40.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這樣還真是令人同情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.02,0:16:43.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}「明明」 「還真是」 這種話是多餘的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.73,0:16:45.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}話說為什麼你們也跟過來了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.02,0:16:48.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}因為我們是超研部員 當然要來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.40,0:16:51.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}而且小田切還是競爭學生會長的人選呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.70,0:16:57.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.82,0:17:02.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那麼就快點讓我變回最初的狀態吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.25,0:17:05.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}應該說「請把我變回去」才對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.21,0:17:06.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}什麼嘛 宮村
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.08,0:17:10.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}會長的評價會上升都是靠我的力量吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.75,0:17:13.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}總之 現在知道你們底牌之後
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.13,0:17:16.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我就不會讓你們隨心所欲了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.55,0:17:18.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那我們會期待著
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.26,0:17:21.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}在把我變回去之前
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.22,0:17:25.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}山田 我有話和你說 讓我們兩個人獨處
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.94,0:17:28.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}什麼啊 有什麼話要說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.48,0:17:31.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真是的 你還真不懂女孩子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.86,0:17:36.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}肯定就是說在我們面前接吻很難為情嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.95,0:17:38.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}小麗 我們去外面吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.07,0:17:40.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯 嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.78,0:17:42.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這就是所謂的 武士的憐憫吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.12,0:17:44.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是吧 五十嵐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.83,0:17:47.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好厲害的…氣場
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.17,0:17:51.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那麼 你要說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.46,0:17:54.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不是要說什麼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.67,0:17:57.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}因為你 讓我吃了不少苦頭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.13,0:17:57.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.30,0:18:00.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}雖說這原本就是因為魅惑能力
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.18,0:18:03.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但是我卻喜歡你到無法自拔
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.22,0:18:06.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不僅上課不能集中注意力
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.64,0:18:08.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}學生會的工作也敷衍了事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.94,0:18:10.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就是因為一直在等著你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.40,0:18:13.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}然而好不容易找到你之後
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.19,0:18:15.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你卻在和白石同學接吻
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.11,0:18:19.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那我們快點恢復原狀吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.28,0:18:23.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}所以 拜託你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.16,0:18:25.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我希望就保持這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.41,0:18:31.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}自己的能力居然可以讓別人如此幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.38,0:18:33.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我至今都不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.00,0:18:39.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}沒關係 我很滿意現在的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.59,0:18:43.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}還是說
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.35,0:18:48.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你不想讓我像現在這樣繼續喜歡你嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.78,0:19:06.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.45,0:19:13.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}因為我 絕對不會喜歡你的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.80,0:19:20.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那男人在說些什麼自大的話啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.14,0:19:23.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}完了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.51,0:19:25.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.47,0:19:27.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這樣這件事就到此為止了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.68,0:19:31.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.94,0:19:37.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}朱雀高中七大不可思議
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.82,0:19:38.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}超研部
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.44,0:19:41.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}為什麼你會有超研部的筆記
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.95,0:19:42.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我在這裡找到的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.78,0:19:45.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}喂 這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.99,0:19:47.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.08,0:19:53.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}在朱雀高中裡 擁有不可思議能力而被稱為魔女的學生
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.75,0:19:56.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那是什麼 讓我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.75,0:20:03.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}根據我們超研部的研究 魔女的能力發現有一下幾類
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.64,0:20:06.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}其一 魅惑的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.30,0:20:09.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}其二 心靈感應的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.85,0:20:11.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}以下 下卷繼續
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.89,0:20:14.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那個 快再給我看看下卷
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.10,0:20:15.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}沒有的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.77,0:20:17.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我們沒有找到
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.32,0:20:25.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這麼說來 除了我們還有擁有其他能力的學生
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.74,0:20:27.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}只能全部找出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.53,0:20:31.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}啥 我可不想再繼續捲入麻煩裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.29,0:20:35.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}笨蛋 沒有你這個魔女發現器 我們要怎麼找啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.96,0:20:37.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}魔女發現器？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.09,0:20:42.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}因為山田是唯一對魔女能力有免疫的人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.63,0:20:46.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我都說了 我已經不想再被捲入到麻煩裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.43,0:20:51.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}正因為如此
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.52,0:20:54.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}正因為如此 我們才要去尋找魔女
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.35,0:20:59.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}山田 你改變了我的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.23,0:21:03.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}小田切一定也是這樣的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.90,0:21:08.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我覺得魔女們一定都希望被你發現
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.46,0:21:18.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}果然還是得白石同學出馬呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.13,0:21:21.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}讓人無法拒絕呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.63,0:21:22.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真拿你們沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.76,0:21:26.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}畢竟是超研部部長白石同學的命令啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.51,0:21:30.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你們要不要也趁此機會入個部啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.22,0:21:32.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一起來尋找魔女吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.93,0:21:36.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我確實很在意魔女的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.85,0:21:37.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.81,0:21:39.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但是我不想入部
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.06,0:21:45.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}因為我覺得自己和你們這些無節操的人合不來
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.20,0:21:48.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}而且我並沒有打算和競爭學生會長的敵人搞好關係
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.16,0:21:51.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那麼讓宮村退部的話 你就會來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.03,0:21:53.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好過分啊 伊藤同學
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.20,0:21:56.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}先說好 現在我是不會道歉的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.46,0:22:01.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我說的是 把那次打架事件的過錯全部都推給你的事
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.71,0:22:03.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}啥
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.96,0:22:05.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就這樣好了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.17,0:22:07.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}難道不是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.13,0:22:14.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我們不就為了過這樣的學校生活才來到這裡的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.98,0:22:18.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}說的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.90,0:23:52.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那個 潮
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.86,0:23:53.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎麼了 小田切
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.66,0:23:55.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}果然還是你最棒
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.66,0:23:55.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\an7}{\fs30}最高（さいこう）有最高和最棒兩層意思
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.32,0:23:56.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你說…什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.28,0:23:59.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}下集 山田君與七魔女 請回答我
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.29,0:24:00.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}什什什什什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.70,0:24:03.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你是我們這裡身高最高的人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.25,0:24:04.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這個意思啊
